 He smilied. The sound of general destructor just appealed to him. "I 
overheard your discussion with Megatron. I am pleased he has agreed to take 
out the alliance. But we still need the maximals. I need you to wait on the 
actual attack. Magatron may still bring his troops now if he wishes but I 
need you to wait for the maximals to join us. They are a vital key."
